text:
This is my honest opinion about TWICE.  These girls enjoy an incredible great fortune.  These members have won the metaphorical "lottery".  But it is even better than "winning an actual lottery".  That just give you money.  Their fortune surpasses such trivial matters.  And it isn't necessarily that they were chosen to be a member of TWICE.  That played a huge role in their great fortune,...but their true fortune lies in their relationships they have with each other.  It is _far_ more precious than "things".  And in my opinion, these types of relationships are better than any romantic ones they may get into.  It is a different level, of course,...but this is how I see it.  And I hope it last for the rest of their lifetime!  

And this comment could also be made about the members of ITZY, as well! 

TWICE, thank you [the members, teams, managers, producers] for creating videos like this.
